character.name:
Isometric pixel art ghoul monster for a 2D RPG game

Undead ghoul creature, thin and hunched posture, long arms, clawed hands.

Pale green / grayish skin, slightly rotten look, visible bones or ribs.

Sunken glowing eyes, sharp teeth, menacing but readable expression.

Wearing torn rags or old clothes, medieval fantasy style.

Isometric 3/4 view, consistent with 64x32 isometric grid, correct proportions for game sprite.

Designed as a game enemy sprite, not an illustration.

Clear silhouette, exaggerated anatomy for readability.

Clean pixel art, sharp pixels, no blur, no smooth gradients.

Limited color palette, hand-crafted pixel shading.

Neutral or transparent background, no ground, no effects, no UI.

Style inspired by Dofus 1.29, classic fantasy RPG monsters.
